"'''Give In to Me'''" 是迈克尔·杰克逊1991年的录音室专辑《[[Dangerous|Dangerous]]》的第十首歌曲。 单曲在新西兰连续四周达到榜首，并在[[英國單曲排行榜|英國單曲排行榜]]排名第二。 风格上， “Give In to Me”是一个[[硬摇滚|硬摇滚]]民谣，其中还有枪炮玫瑰乐队吉他手slash伴奏.<ref name="campbell (1993) 309">{{Cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=BVC9zltjf-EC&source=gbs_navlinks_s|title=Michael Jackson: The King of Pop|last=Campbell|first=Lisa|publisher=Branden Books|accessdate=October 16, 2010|year=1993|isbn=978-0-8283-1957-7|page=309|archive-date=2016-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160729181339/https://books.google.com/books?id=BVC9zltjf-EC&source=gbs_navlinks_s|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="hamilton dangerous">{{Cite news|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/thestar/access/515018501.html?dids=515018501:515018501&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Nov+22%2C+1991&author=Nick+Krewen&pub=The+Spectator&desc=Shrewd+and+Dangerous&pqatl=google|title=Shrewd and Dangerous|last=Krewen|first=Nick|date=November 22, 1991|newspaper=The Hamilton Spectator|accessdate=October 16, 2010|quote=Jackson also wants to reach a rock audience, so Guns 'N' Roses guitarist Slash contributes his two cents in Black Or White and Give In To Me, while Heavy D. splices in some rap at appropriate moments|archive-date=2012-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121104064243/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/thestar/access/515018501.html?dids=515018501:515018501&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Nov+22,+1991&author=Nick+Krewen&pub=The+Spectator&desc=Shrewd+and+Dangerous&pqatl=google|dead-url=no}}</ref> 有些人认为这首歌，也可以被认为有激进的性暗示的[[重金属|重金属]]民谣，.<ref name="Atlantic (1992) 101">{{Cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=iMkmAQAAIAAJ&q=%22Give+In+to+Me%22+heavy+metal&dq=%22Give+In+to+Me%22+heavy+metal&hl=en&ei=XrrdTKKFAcP_lge5tpWRDQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CB8Q6AEwAA|title=The Atlantic, Volume 269|last=|first=|publisher=Atlantic Monthly Co|accessdate=November 12, 2010|year=1992|isbn=|page=101|archive-date=2016-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160801202106/https://books.google.com/books?id=iMkmAQAAIAAJ&q=%22Give+In+to+Me%22+heavy+metal&dq=%22Give+In+to+Me%22+heavy+metal&hl=en&ei=XrrdTKKFAcP_lge5tpWRDQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CB8Q6AEwAA|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="campbell (1993) 325-326">{{Cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=BVC9zltjf-EC&source=gbs_navlinks_s|title=Michael Jackson: The King of Pop|last=Campbell|first=Lisa|publisher=Branden Books|accessdate=December 7, 2010|year=1993|isbn=978-0-8283-1957-7|pages=325–326|archive-date=2016-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160729181339/https://books.google.com/books?id=BVC9zltjf-EC&source=gbs_navlinks_s|dead-url=no}}</ref> 单曲从未在北美和亚洲发行。单曲发行值得注意的是它的B边，其中包括杰克逊两个的其他[[硬摇滚|硬摇滚]]歌曲， “[[Dirty_Diana|Dirty Diana]]”，专辑中的版本“[[Beat_It|Beat It]]”，这也包括硬摇滚吉他手的客串（分别是[[史蒂夫·史蒂文斯|史蒂夫·史蒂文斯]]和[[埃迪·范·海伦|埃迪·范·海伦]]）。

== 背景 ==
 这首歌曲为E小调的基础音。杰克逊的声音的跨度是从G3到B4。它具有每分钟87次中度慢节奏。
